Name: EQUIPMENT DESIGNATOR
Explanation: THE STANDARD DESIGNATOR OF A TYPE OF EQUIPMENT IN USE IN THE NATO FORCES.

Name: MAIN PSYOP EQUIPMENT
Explanation: THE PRIMARY TYPE OF EQUIPMENT THAT IS EMPLOYED BY A PSYOP UNIT.

Name: SHELTER TYPE GENERATION DESIGNATOR
Explanation: DENOTES WHETHER A SHELTER IS OF THE FIRST, SECOND, THIRD, ETC, GENERATION.

Name: TYPE OF SUPPORT EQUIPMENT
Explanation: THE TYPE OF SUPPORT EQUIPMENT REQUIRED.

Name: REPLENISHMENT RIG
Explanation: THE BASIC TYPE OF RIG EMPLOYED IN UNDERWAY REPLENISHMENT OPERATIONS.

Name: EQUIPMENT TYPE AFFECTED BY ECM OR INTERFERENCE
Explanation: ECM IS ELECTRONIC COUNTERMEASURE.

Name: TYPE OF SECURE VOICE EQUIPMENT
Explanation: THE NATO NOMENCLATURE OF SECURE VOICE EQUIPMENTS I.A.W. ATP 29.

Name: TYPE OF CRYPTOGRAPHIC EQUIPMENT
Explanation: THE TYPE OF COMMUNICATIONS ENCRYPTION EQUIPMENT HELD.

Name: TONE KEY TYPE
Explanation: SEE CODES IN ATP 29.

Name: TYPE OF FREQUENCY SHIFT CONVERTER
Explanation: THE TYPE OF FREQUENCY SHIFT CONVERTER FROM ATP 29.

Name: RADAR WARNING RECEIVER TYPE
Explanation: THE TYPE OF RADAR WARNING RECEIVING DEVICE A SPECIFIC AIRCRAFT IS EQUIPPED WITH.

Name: EMITTER TYPE
Explanation: THE TYPE OF EQUIPMENT THAT IS THE SOURCE OF A PARTICULAR EMITTED SIGNAL.

Name: EQUIPMENT FAMILY
Explanation: REFLECTS THE MAJOR GENERIC TYPE OF EQUIPMENT.

Name: EQUIPMENT SUB-FAMILY
Explanation: REFLECTS THE SUB-CATEGORIZATION OF THE MAJOR GENERIC TYPES OF EQUIPMENT. DATA ITEMS AND DATA CODES ARE TO BE TAKEN FROM AINTP-3, VOLUME 2 (DATA DICTIONARY).

Name: SURFACE-TO-AIR WEAPON RESOURCE TYPE
Explanation: ONE OF THE COMPONENTS OF A SURFACE TO AIR WEAPON, EITHER A LAUNCHER OR A FIRE CONTROL UNIT.

Name: EQUIPMENT TYPE, EXPANDED
Explanation: INDICATES THE TYPE OR TYPE-GROUPING TO WHICH THE SPECIFIC EQUIPMENT BELONGS.

Name: REPLENISHMENT RIG END FITTING OR COUPLING
Explanation: THE TYPE OF REPLENISHMENT RIG, END FITTING OR COUPLING, REQUIRED TO BE USED AT THE SPECIFIED STATION.

Name: REPLENISHMENT RIG END FITTING
Explanation: THE END FITTING TO BE USED FOR THE SPECIFIED STATION-TO-STATION TRANSFER.

Name: TYPE OF EOD RECOGNITION EQUIPMENT
Explanation: THE TYPE OF EOD RECOGNITION EQUIPMENT HELD.

Name: TYPE OF EOD NEUTRALIZATION EQUIPMENT
Explanation: THE TYPE OF EOD NEUTRALIZATION EQUIPMENT HELD.

Name: TYPE OF SHELTER MATERIAL
Explanation: THE TYPE OF SHELTER MATERIAL.

Name: TYPE OF TENTAGE
Explanation: THE TYPE OF TENTAGE.

Name: GOB EQUIPMENT TYPE
Explanation: PROVIDES A GROUND ORDER OF BATTLE (GOB) EQUIPMENT TYPE DESIGNATOR TAKEN FROM THE LISTING PRODUCED FOR THE GROUND ORDER CONFERENCE AUTOMATION SYSTEM (GROCAS).

Name: TYPE OF WATER CONTAINER
Explanation: THE TYPE OF CONTAINER USED FOR TRANSPORTING THE WATER.

Name: THREAT WEAPON TYPES IDENTIFIED
Explanation: THE TYPE OF THREAT WEAPONS IDENTIFIED.

Name: MCM EQUIPMENT
Explanation: THE TYPE OF MCM EQUIPMENT IN ACCORDANCE WITH ATP-1 VOL 2 TABLE Y.

Name: TYPE OF WATER FILTRATION EQUIPMENT
Explanation: THE TYPE OF WATER FILTRATION EQUIPMENT AVAILABLE.

Name: TYPE OF WATER ANALYSIS EQUIPMENT
Explanation: THE TYPE OF WATER ANALYSIS EQUIPMENT AVAILABLE.

Name: ADDITIONAL HELICOPTER STORES
Explanation: TYPES OF NON AMMUNITION OPERATIONAL STORES THAT CAN BE CARRIED BY A HELICOPTER.

Name: FREQUENCY FUNCTIONAL USE TYPE
Explanation: THE PRIMARY FUNCTIONAL USE TYPE OF A FREQUENCY OF A RADIO/RADAR SYSTEM.

Name: COUNTERMEASURES EQUIPMENT
Explanation: THE TYPE OF COUNTERMEASURES EQUIPMENT INSTALLED ON REPORTED MISSION AIRCRAFT.

Name: COUNTERMEASURES DISPENSER
Explanation: THE TYPE OF COUNTERMEASURE DISPENSER INSTALLED ON REPORTED MISSION AIRCRAFT.

Name: TOWED DECOYS
Explanation: THE TYPE OF DECOYS TOWED DURING MISSION OPERATIONS.

Name: MATRIX CAPABILITIES
Explanation: THE TYPE OF COUNTERMEASURES LINKING SYSTEM INSTALLED ON REPORTED MISSION AIRCRAFT.

Name: TARGETING AND OR NAVIGATION POD
Explanation: THE SPECIFIC TYPE OF TARGETING AND/OR NAVIGATION POD EMPLOYED BY TASKED MISSION AIRCRAFT.

Name: EMERGENCY COMMUNICATIONS BEACON TYPE
Explanation: EMERGENCY COMMUNICATIONS BEACON TYPE.
